*   On the head of [Pungoteague](/Pungoteague_Creek), at Addison's landing; at Pitt's landing, upon [Pokomoke](/Pocomoke_River); at [Guilford](/Guilford,_Virginia), at Mr. Andrew's warehouse landing, in the county of Accomack, under one inspection.

